To print CRM Analytics dashboards: 
Use CRM Analytics
Printing is available in the dashboard preview mode in CRM Analytics Studio.
Click to open the menu, and select Print Preview.
A snapshot of your dashboard opens.
Click Print to open your browserâ€™s print dialog, where you can send the image to your printer or save it as a PDF file.
